=document.getElementById("search-value").value;console.log(e),window.location.href="/asdf"}));</script><ul class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 menu"><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../index5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Home</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/business5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Business</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/politics5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Politics</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/nigeria5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Nigeria</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/health5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Health &amp; Wellbeing</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/education5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Education</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/lifestyle5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Life &amp; Style</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/sport5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Sport</span></div></a></li><li class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 "><a class="link" href="../../../../category/editorial5593.html?amp=1"><div class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323 title"><span class="jsx-db8ff9fbf4c70323">Editorial</span></div></a>